title: Lil Baby Interview/ Four Black Women in Politics and more
itunes:title: Lil Baby Interview/ Four Black Women in Politics and more
description:
Monday 12/3 - Today on the show we had Lil Baby stop by where he spoke about releasing his album "Street Gossip", leaving the streets and more. Also we had the authors of the book "Four Colored Girls Who Considered Politics" who spoke about their experience in politics and how it has changed politics in America. Also, we allowed listeners to call up and nominate anyone they would like for "Donkey of the Day". 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
